### Chainverse SDK

[Chainverse SDK Android](https://github.com/Chainverse/android-sdk)

[Chainverse SDK iOS](https://github.com/Chainverse/ios-sdk)
### 1. Mô hình
[![name](https://i.imgur.com/0nXfikL.png)](https://i.imgur.com/0nXfikL.png)

### 2. CÁC HÀM API MỞ RA ĐỂ DEV GỌI
- API init:
   + iOS:`[[ChainverseSDK shared] init:@"developerAddress" gameAddress:@"gameAddress"];`
   + Android:`ChainverseSDK.getInstance().init("developerAddress", "gameAddress");`
- API Connect với Trust Wallet:
   + iOS:`[[ChainverseSDK shared] connectTrust];`
   + Android:`ChainverseSDK.getInstance().connectTrust();`
- API Transfer với Trust Wallet:
   + iOS:`[[ChainverseSDK shared] transferTrust:@"asset"
                                       to:@"to"
                                   amount:@"amount"
                                 feePrice:@"feePrice"
                                 feeLimit:@"feeLimit"];`
   + Android:`ChainverseSDK.getInstance().transferTrust("asset","to","amount","feePrice","feeLimit");`
- API để hứng callback từ Trust Wallet:
   + iOS:`[[ChainverseSDK shared] scene:scene openURLContexts:URLContexts];`
   + Android:`ChainverseSDK.getInstance().handleResult(intent);`

### 3. SCHEMA
#### 3.1. Connect với Trust Wallet
##### 3.1.1 SDK Connect với Trust Wallet bẳng scheme url
- URL: trust://sdk_get_accounts?coins.0={COINS.0}&coins.1={COINS.0}&app={APP_SCHEME}&callback={CALLBACK}&id=1
- `APP_SCHEME`: Khai báo app scheme để Trust Wallet callback lại app.
- `COINS.0, COINS.1`: Mạng lưới blockchain (BCS, ETH)
- `CALLBACK`: Loại callback Trust Wallet sẽ trả về

##### 3.1.2 Trust Wallet open (callback) Game bẳng scheme url
- URL: `{APP_SCHEME}://sdk_sign_result?accounts={DATA_ACCOUNT}&id=1`
- `APP_SCHEME`: Khai báo app scheme để Trust Wallet callback lại app.
- `DATA_ACCOUNT`: Data từ Trust Wallet trả về

#### 3.2. Transfer với Trust Wallet
##### 3.2.1 SDK transfer với Trust Wallet bẳng scheme url
- URL: trust://sdk_transaction?action=transfer&amount={AMOUNT}&asset={ASSET}&confirm_type=sign&fee_limit={FEE_LIMIT}&fee_price={FEE_PRICE}&nonce=447&to={TO}&app={APP_SCHEME}&callback=sdk_sign_result&id=3
- `AMOUNT`: Số coin cần chuyển.
- `ASSET`: Mạng lưới blockchain (BCS, ETH)
- `FEE_LIMIT`: Phí.
- `FEE_PRICE`: Phí.
- `TO`: Địa chỉ chuyển coin.
- `APP_SCHEME`: Khai báo app scheme để Trust Wallet callback lại app.